    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>The encodeUnicodeString static method of Zend_Json_Encoder is missing.
It is called into the new method Zend_Json::_recursiveJsonExprFinder</p>

<p>Here is a fix :</p>

<pre class="highlight"><code>
public static function encodeUnicodeString($string) {
    $encoder = new self();
    return substr($encoder-&gt;_encodeString($string), 1, -1);
}
</code></pre>

